headline: Tesla eyes internal CEO candidates if Musk steps down over pay vote, Bloomberg News reports

The development underscores how central Musk remains to Tesla's identity and investor confidence, even as it faces pressure to reduce dependence on him.  Tesla did not immediately respond to a Reuters request for comment.
